{"log":{"pages":[], "comment":"exported @ 2026/3/25 16:46:23", "entries":[{"time":866, "connection":"ClientPort:0;EgressPort:50309", "request":{"headersSize":462, "postData":{"text":"", "mimeType":""}, "queryString":[{"name":"ver", "value":"5.0.20253.3311"}, {"name":"tele", "value":"true"}, {"name":"meta", "value":"true"}], "headers":[{"name":"User-Agent", "value":"Fiddler/5.0.20253.3311 (.NET 4.8; WinNT 10.0.26200.0; zh-CN; 16xAMD64; Auto Update; Full Instance; Extensions: APITesting, AutoSaveExt, EventLog, FiddlerOrchestraAddon, HostsFile, RulesTab2, SAZClipboardFactory, SimpleFilter, Timeline)"}, {"name":"Pragma", "value":"no-cache"}, {"name":"Host", "value":"api.getfiddler.com"}, {"name":"Accept-Language", "value":"zh-CN"}, {"name":"Accept-Encoding", "value":"gzip, deflate"}, {"name":"Connection", "value":"close"}], "bodySize":0, "url":"https://api.getfiddler.com/fc/latest?ver=5.0.20253.3311&tele=true&meta=true", "cookies":[], "method":"GET", "httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1"}, "timings":{"blocked":-1, "ssl":618, "receive":3, "wait":245, "dns":0, "send":0, "connect":618}, "response":{"headersSize":760, "bodySize":2595, "statusText":"OK", "redirectURL":"", "status":200, "httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1", "cookies":[], "content":{"compression":1536, "text":"5\r\n0\r\n20253\r\n3311\r\n\r\n5.0.20253.3311 [31/03/2025]\r\nfixes:\r\n Application crashes on minimize\r\n\r\n5.0.20252.3251 [27/03/2025]\r\nfixes:\r\n Transcoder fails to load\r\n Consent dialog looks broken on high-DPI screens\r\n Update banner styles for unsupported functionalities\r\n Update third party dependencies to mitigate potential security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n5.0.20251.1171 [30/01/2025]\r\nfeatures:\r\n Add digital signature verification for external files.\r\n Show a confirmation dialog before loading unverified files.\r\n Show a confirmation dialog before opening files in an external application.\r\nfixes:\r\n Replace obsolete DotNetZip dependency with SharpZipLib.\r\n Update third party dependencies to mitigate potential security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n5.0.20245.10105 [17/10/2024]\r\nfeatures:\r\n Remove articles and banners from the \"Getting started\" page. \r\n Remove \"Offer for beta\" option. \r\nfixes:\r\n Update third party dependencies to mitigate potential security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n5.0.20244.10953 [06/08/2024]\r\nfixes:\r\n Update backend URLs for surveys\r\n Update third party dependencies to mitigate potential security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n5.0.20243.10853 [16/05/2024]\r\nfixes:\r\n Check for updates fails in the beta channel.\r\n Update third party dependencies to mitigate potential security vulnerabilities.\r\n\r\n5.0.20242.10753 [27/03/2024]\r\nfeatures:\r\n Show informational banners in cases where some functionalities are not supported\r\n Add tls1.1 and tls1.2 in the default HTTPS supported protocols for decryption (for new installations only)\r\n\r\nfixes:\r\n Changing fonts breaks the TextView tab by hiding the search option\r\n Saving SAZ file fails when there are more than 62K sessions\r\n Check for update fails when tls1.2 is not added in the HTTPS supported protocols\r\n Host Remapping tool fails to override certificate behavior for requests created by Fiddler Classic\r\n Export as cURL uses -d instead of --data-raw which causes security issues in some rare cases\r\n An unnecessary log is printed when ClientHello's length is greater than 255 bytes\r\n\r\n5.0.20211.51073 [15/12/2021]\r\nfeatures:\r\n Change the name to Progress Telerik Fiddler Classic\r\n Add Cross-Origin headers to Response Header Security section\r\n Throw HTTP protocol violation when a header name contains a space\r\n\r\nfixes:\r\n TLS ClientHello and ServerHello parsing fails when there are large extensions\r\n Change the validity period for dynamically created certificates in Fiddler Classic to be less than an year\r\n Update Set-Cookie header template as it is expired\r\n HostnameIs method might return true even when host does not match when it has port\r\n Incorrectly strips Authorization header if it happens to contain the letters NTLM\r\n Fiddler Auth Inspector should decode BASIC credentials using Encoding.UTF8\r\n Error window at launch may be hard to find\r\n TLS Handshake Analyzer omits the last value in the supported_versions extension\r\n Process picker option is not working for Chromium based browsers\r\n \"Set AutoResponder comment\" hotkey moves list selection\r\n\r\n\r\n5.0.20204.45441 [11/03/2020]\r\nfixes:\r\n Fix Copy | Session menu item in the Web Sessions List context menu.\r\n Fix Copy | Headers menu item in the Web Sessions List context menu.\r\n Remove the possibility to start a local executable without user's permission: CVE-2020-13661, reported by Lion Nagenrauft, nagenrauft-consulting.com\r\n\r\n5.0.20202.18177 [04/21/2020]\r\nfeatures:\r\n \"Accept all CONNECTs\" option in AutoResponder\r\n\r\nfixes:\r\n Quick filters - removed filter cannot be reapplied\r\n Various bugfixes and improvements\r\n\r\n5.0.20194.41348 [10/03/2019]\r\nfeatures:\r\n Ability to preserve filters in Fiddler\r\n New GetStarted tab\r\n Ability to group AutoResponder rules\r\n Fiddler recognizes MSEdge and Brave as web browsers\r\n New preference fiddler.knownbrowsers - comma-separated list with processes that Fiddler recognizes as browsers\r\n\r\nfixes:\r\n Ctrl+Shift+C and Ctrl+C shortcuts do not copy\r\n m shortcut changes selection in AutoResponder tab\r\n Minor bug fixes\r\n\r\n@WELCOME@\r\nAre you sweating on building JavaScript UI?\r\n\r\nSpeed up your development by using Kendo UI library for your next project - http://prgress.co/2swAPLK\r\n", "size":4131, "mimeType":"text/plain"}, "headers":[{"name":"Content-Type", "value":"text/plain"}, {"name":"Transfer-Encoding", "value":"chunked"}, {"name":"Connection", "value":"close"}, {"name":"Date", "value":"Wed, 25 Mar 2026 08:44:54 GMT"}, {"name":"Signature", "value":"SignedHeaders=content-type;x-date, Signature=AAAAWzBZMBMGByqGSM49AgEGCCqGSM49AwEHA0IABNsAzGwa7Q3iTZFqv3xYHemw/qxkwk0sIC/usJVi7713VJv0B1JbfuiDXxHfScNyyQjkuaHKtwbn5qUeHjFwpGbBAPO6SUvQuFISh4kuZnyPs2yV0o5GTKBkQQ1ii3ZQyq3ImpTuLvXHIAbkSHlWDJJ8f3CQCbdaVZqUClU1vvXv"}, {"name":"api-supported-versions", "value":"1.0"}, {"name":"Server", "value":"Kestrel"}, {"name":"Content-Encoding", "value":"gzip"}, {"name":"Vary", "value":"Accept-Encoding"}, {"name":"X-Date", "value":"Wed, 25 Mar 2026 08:44:54 GMT"}, {"name":"X-Cache", "value":"Miss from cloudfront"}, {"name":"Via", "value":"1.1 9ed589723d880832fbd56a7bfede4018.cloudfront.net (CloudFront)"}, {"name":"X-Amz-Cf-Pop", "value":"LAX54-P1"}, {"name":"Alt-Svc", "value":"h3=\":443\"; ma=86400"}, {"name":"X-Amz-Cf-Id", "value":"QkjJhwM6IxecWFK73NwfbhDgMytpQtxIjqi7kFf3xWduiauwrZalMQ=="}]}, "startedDateTime":"2026-03-25T16:44:53.6753361+08:00", "cache":{}}, {"time":25, "connection":"ClientPort:0;EgressPort:50309", "request":{"headersSize":324, "postData":{"text":"", "mimeType":""}, "queryString":[], "headers":[{"name":"Host", "value":"api.getfiddler.com:443"}, {"name":"User-Agent", "value":"Fiddler/5.0.20253.3311 (.NET 4.8; WinNT 10.0.26200.0; zh-CN; 16xAMD64; Auto Update; Full Instance; Extensions: APITesting, AutoSaveExt, EventLog, FiddlerOrchestraAddon, HostsFile, RulesTab2, SAZClipboardFactory, SimpleFilter, Timeline)"}], "bodySize":0, "url":"http://api.getfiddler.com:443", "cookies":[], "method":"CONNECT", "httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1"}, "timings":{"blocked":-1, "ssl":0, "receive":11, "wait":9, "dns":0, "send":4, "connect":1}, "response":{"headersSize":41, "bodySize":0, "statusText":"Connection established", "redirectURL":"", "status":200, "httpVersion":"HTTP/1.1", "cookies":[], "content":{"compression":0, "encoding":"base64", "size":0, "mimeType":"", "text":""}, "headers":[]}, "startedDateTime":"2026-03-25T16:44:53.7082595+08:00", "cache":{}}, {"time":141, "connection":"ClientPort:62048;EgressPort:62049", "request":{"headersSize":284, "postData":{"text":"A SSLv3-compatible ClientHello handshake was found. Fiddler extracted the parameters below